        "headline": "Hazardous Materials Warning issued March 17 at 1:18PM PDT until March 17 at 9:18PM PDT by NWS Medford OR",
        "description": "...Hwy 97 Closed in Dorris Due to Hazmat...\n\nThe following message is transmitted at the request of Siskiyou County.\n\n***For passenger vehicles only***\n\nNorth Bound Traffic Reroute due to road closure on Hwy 97 in Dorris. Alternate Route: From Northbound Hwy97... Turn East on Shady Dell Rd... North on E. Butte Vly Rd... North on Dorris/Brown Rd... North on Center St to Hwy 97.\n\n*** Passenger Vehicles Only ***\n\n***For passenger vehicles only***\n\nNorth Bound Traffic Reroute due to road closure on Hwy 97 in Dorris. Alternate Route: From Northbound Hwy97... Turn East on Shady Dell Rd... North on E. Butte Vly Rd... North on Dorris/Brown Rd... North on Center St to Hwy 97.\n\n*** Passenger Vehicles Only ***\n\n&&\n\nLAT...LON 4200 12190 4200 12188 4194 12193 4194 12195\n\n$$\n\n17737787150001393522449",
